title: Starbound.Beta.1.Update.Irritated.Koala-neO
description:
Release Date: 13/12/06
Version: Irritated Koala

This release Contains ONLY the update files!
Crack is now fixed.
Includes all other previous updates.

Install:
Run the installer as admin
Select previous installation of starbound
Install, then play.
Run all game executables as administrator

Troubleshoot:
If not starting try:
  -Closing Steam.
  -Installing DirectX
  -Reinstalling game.


Multiplayer works over lan, and if ports are forwarded over internet.



Don't forget to keep seeding! My connection is not the best atm! >:c
